## Security Notice

This software handles sensitive security credentials. While the software 
implements industry-standard security practices and cryptographic algorithms,
no software can guarantee absolute security. Users accept full responsibility
for the security of their data and should:

1. Use strong, unique master passwords
2. Keep regular encrypted backups
3. Keep the software updated
4. Report security vulnerabilities responsibly
5. Understand the security model before use

For security concerns, please review SECURITY.md and follow responsible
disclosure practices.
